asset.hookText:
http://www.campchef.com/flat-top-grill.html

Cooking a lot of food is easy when using Camp Chef's Flat Top Grill. The large surface area will enhance your cooking experience giving you plenty of room to work. Included is an interchangeable professional flat top griddle making it easy to cook pancakes and eggs, then switch to grilled burgers for the next meal. Four individual burners simply control heat in specific areas creating heat zones that will help you manage hot foods. The folding side shelves and roller wheels are added for convenience.
